targets.query: SELECT "value" FROM "node_time_seconds","node_boot_time_seconds" WHERE ("car" =~ /^$car$/) AND $timeFilter FILL(previous)
SELECT last("value") FROM "node_boot_time_seconds" WHERE ("car" =~ /^$car$/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT "value" FROM "probe_success","script_success" WHERE ("car" =~ /^$car$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "description"
SELECT last("value") FROM "probe_success","script_success" WHERE ("car" =~ /^$car$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "description" ORDER BY time DESC
